  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Start the day with a breakfast buffet in the Hotel Savica, with hot and cold options that will set you up perfectly for the day. </p>
<p>Your half board evening meal is enjoyed in the neighbouring Hotel Rikli Balance where you'll have a delicious three course buffet. Fresh local ingredients are used to create a menu of Slovenian and international dishes.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
