  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Garni Hotel Savica is perfectly located in the centre of Bled, only 250 metres from the lake. Excellent hospitality is combined with access to the fantastic wellness facilities of the <a data-udi="umb://document/94de03fc3b9f42eaadf51b5041aee5ac" href="/{localLink:umb://document/94de03fc3b9f42eaadf51b5041aee5ac}" title="Hotel Rikli Balance">Rikli Balance Hotel</a>, where you'll also enjoy your half-board evening meal.</p>
<h2>Comfy, air-conditioned rooms</h2>
<p>You have everything you need for a comfortable stay at the Garni Hotel Savica - air-conditioned rooms are available as twins or doubles, and have a minibar fridge and tea/coffee making facilities, plus a balcony to enjoy the view. There's a family-friendly ambience and children's playroom for the little ones.</p>
<h2>Relax in the Živa Wellness Centre</h2>
<p>Make the most of your daily access to the <span>Živa Wellness Centre at the neighbouring Rikli Balance Hotel, for a spot of relaxation. Every day, you can use the swimming pool facilities for up to three hours - it's the largest pool complex in Bled with four indoor thermal pools, an outdoor pool, massage pool and waterslide. For the ultimate in relaxation, treat yourself to some time in the excellent sauna area (payable locally). Beauty and massage treatments are available to book locally, too.</span></p>]]></description>
