  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Spa &amp; wellness facilities</strong></p>
<p>Every day you can enjoy one three-hour free admission to the Živa Wellness Centre's pools. Use of the sauna facilities is payable locally.</p>
<ul>
<li>Pool facilities include four indoor thermal pools, a children’s thermal pool, an outdoor thermal pool, an indoor waterslide, and a massage pool</li>
<li>Sauna facilities include three Turkish saunas, three Finnish saunas, two cold pools, and an experience shower (payable locally)</li>
<li>Relaxation area</li>
<li>Spa &amp; beauty treatments (payable locally)</li>
<li>Pool towels (payable locally)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Additional facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Parking (payable locally)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Family facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Cots are available for €10 per night</li>
<li>Children's playroom (unsupervised)</li>
<li>Children's pool in the Živa Wellness Centre</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
